data.description: New listing Raised Ranch 1660 square feet 3 bedrooms 1.5 baths plus a 2 car garage. On the main floor, there is an open kitchen design with nice appliances(New Dishwasher being Installed) a dining room with access to a very large deck, nice laminate wood floors, 3 bedrooms, and a full hall bath. Downstairs there is a large family room with a slider to the yard, a large den that the seller used as as bedroom in the past. There is a nice 1/2 bath, laundry room, and a 2-car garage. This home is 2 minutes to Route 9 Shopping and train stations are all within 10 minutes. Make your appointment today and make this home yours.
